<blockquote>
  <p>What is patriotism, but nostalgia for the foods of our youth?”</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Recently, I’ve been feeling very <strong>nostalgic</strong>. The extended time at home has stirred that yearning for the past, for younger years. It’s inspired by the craving for the foods I grew up on, the music that filled my afternoons, and the stories that shaped the way I see the world.</p>

